<section xmlns="https://code.dccouncil.us/schemas/dc-library" xmlns:codified="https://code.dccouncil.us/schemas/codified" xmlns:codify="https://code.dccouncil.us/schemas/codify" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude" containing-doc="D.C. Code">
  <num>7-2502.14</num>
  <heading>Registration of self-defense sprays.</heading>
  <para>
    <num>(a)</num>
    <text>A person 18 years of age or older must register the self-defense spray at the time of purchase by completing a standard registration form.</text>
  </para>
  <para>
    <num>(b)</num>
    <text>The vendor must forward the registration form to the Metropolitan Police Department.</text>
  </para>
